Available Tools: share_file | set_permissions | get_shared_link | revoke_access | list_collaborators
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "file_id": "string", "user_email": "string", "permission": "view|comment|edit", "expires_at": "string" }
Response Schema: { "file_id": "string", "shared_link": "string", "collaborators": [{ "email": "string", "permission": "string" }] }
---
Question: Send the Q4 sales forecast to alex.rivera@sales.net with edit permissions ending next Friday.
Call: { "func_call": "share_file", "file_id": "sales_forecast_q4_2024.xlsx", "user_email": "alex.rivera@sales.net", "permission": "edit", "expires_at": "2024-12-20T17:00:00Z" }
Response: { "file_id": "sales_forecast_q4_2024.xlsx", "shared_link": "https://storage.corp.com/s/k8l9m-nop", "collaborators": [{ "email": "alex.rivera@sales.net", "permission": "edit" }] }

Question: Allow the external auditor to view the compliance logs without modification rights for 30 days.
Call: { "func_call": "set_permissions", "file_id": "compliance_logs_2024.csv", "user_email": "auditor@external-firm.com", "permission": "view", "expires_at": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z" }
Response: { "file_id": "compliance_logs_2024.csv", "shared_link": "https://storage.corp.com/s/q1w2e-r3t", "collaborators": [{ "email": "auditor@external-firm.com", "permission": "view" }] }

Question: Let the copywriter add comments to the ad campaign script, access expiring in 4 hours.
Call: { "func_call": "share_file", "file_id": "ad_campaign_script_v5.docx", "user_email": "copywriter@agency.io", "permission": "comment", "expires_at": "2024-11-15T18:00:00Z" }
Response: { "file_id": "ad_campaign_script_v5.docx", "shared_link": "https://storage.corp.com/s/y4u5i-o6p", "collaborators": [{ "email": "copywriter@agency.io", "permission": "comment" }] }

Question: Create a permanent shared link for the company handbook and assign it to the onboarding coordinator.
Call: { "func_call": "get_shared_link", "file_id": "company_handbook_2025.pdf", "user_email": "onboarding@corp.com", "permission": "view", "expires_at": "2099-12-31T23:59:59Z" }
Response: { "file_id": "company_handbook_2025.pdf", "shared_link": "https://storage.corp.com/s/a7s8d-f9g", "collaborators": [{ "email": "onboarding@corp.com", "permission": "view" }] }

Question: Immediately revoke access for the former intern jane.doe@university.edu from the research database.
Call: { "func_call": "revoke_access", "file_id": "research_db_dump.sql", "user_email": "jane.doe@university.edu", "permission": "view", "expires_at": "2024-11-15T00:00:00Z" }
Response: { "file_id": "research_db_dump.sql", "shared_link": "https://storage.corp.com/s/revoked-link", "collaborators": [] }

Question: Display all users with access to the mobile app wireframes and confirm the lead designer has edit rights.
Call: { "func_call": "list_collaborators", "file_id": "mobile_app_wireframes.fig", "user_email": "lead_designer@corp.com", "permission": "edit", "expires_at": "2025-06-01T00:00:00Z" }
Response: { "file_id": "mobile_app_wireframes.fig", "shared_link": "https://storage.corp.com/s/z1x2c-v3b", "collaborators": [{ "email": "lead_designer@corp.com", "permission": "edit" }, { "email": "ux_researcher@corp.com", "permission": "comment" }] }

